  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 3</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You must be able to charge the target in order to use this technique. You swiftly attack the target and return to your previous position, all in the blink of an eye. Make a single attack with a held weapon, which gains Kawarimi Defense 1 and cannot score a critical hit. The firs time this technique is used against a target in a 24 hour period, they are considered flat-footed against the attack, but you cannot apply more sneak attack dice than your Intelligence modifier +1 (maximum 5).<br><br>If the target was already flat-footed, this does not count as a 24-hourly use (for the purpose of the above), and there is no limit to how many sneak attack dice you may apply. A successful Hide check makes it appear as though you hadn't moved at all (Spot check negates).</p>\n\n\n\n",
